  MdePkg/MdePkg.dec
  OneSiliconPkg/SiPkg.dec
  EcFeaturePkg/EcFeaturePkg.dec
  DptfFeaturePkg/DptfFeaturePkg.dec
  PantherLakePlatSamplePkg/PlatformPkg.dec
  PantherLakeBoardPkg/BoardPkg.dec          ## @todo: Remove BoardPkg dependency.

